---
const bookingUrl =
  "https://edmontonsprings.cps.golf/onlineresweb/search-teetime?TeeOffTimeMin=0&TeeOffTimeMax=23";
---

<section id="about" class="relative isolate overflow-hidden bg-pine-900 text-white">
  <img
    src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/4e1033_389d596e6e314cfab11c6100152d4a11~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_1200,h_654,al_c,q_85,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,enc_avif,quality_auto/Green%2018%20toward%2010.jpg"
    alt="Green 18 toward 10 at Edmonton Springs Golf Course"
    class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover"
    loading="eager"
    fetchpriority="high"
    decoding="async"
  />
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-pine-900/55 via-pine-900/70 to-pine-900/95"></div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 sm:py-20 lg:py-24">
    <p class="mb-4 inline-flex rounded-full border border-clubred-100/30 bg-clubred-700/75 px-4 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white">
      Opening about April 22
    </p>
    <h1 class="max-w-4xl font-display text-4xl font-bold uppercase leading-tight sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
      Edmonton Springs Golf Course
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-100 sm:text-lg">
      Our goal is to make your golf experience more enjoyable every time you visit us. We want you to come out and
      experience our great course, great greens and see the changes we have made to improve your golf experience in
      our wonderful surroundings. Under new management with lower prices, new tee boxes and a commitment to the best
      golfer experience.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-center">
      <a
        href={bookingUrl}
        target="_blank"
        rel="noreferrer noopener"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-clubred-500 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-white hover:bg-clubred-700"
      >
        Book a Tee Time
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://www.edmontonspringsgolf.com/email-me"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-white/60 bg-black/20 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-white hover:bg-white/10"
      >
        Join Email List
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
      <p class="rounded-md border border-white/30 bg-white/10 p-4 text-sm font-semibold">
        Expanded Driving Range.
      </p>
      <p class="rounded-md border border-white/30 bg-white/10 p-4 text-sm font-semibold">
        The course is in excellent shape with new larger tee boxes.
      </p>
      <p class="rounded-md border border-white/30 bg-white/10 p-4 text-sm font-semibold">
        9 minute tee times in the afternoon to reduce congestion.
      </p>
      <p class="rounded-md border border-white/30 bg-white/10 p-4 text-sm font-semibold">
        New greens fees still emphasize great rates for this awesome course.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
